<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/950579-i-d-like-to-read-about-the-immigrant-story">I&#39;d like to read about the immigrant story in another state other than California. Can anyone recommend a story about Mexican/Hispanic immigrants in other parts of the United States? Thanks in advance.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_950579'><a id="like_count_community_question_950579" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/950579?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F24731.The_Tortilla_Curtain">like</a></span>

